OL,3,C'Hope is all we had': Man reunited
OL,4,Cwith brother-in-law held hostage by
OL,5,CHamas
OL,7,F"The first thing I did was throw my
OL,8,Farms around him, hugged him, and told
OL,9,Fhim that I loved him.
OL,11,F"His first words to me were, 'I'm
OL,12,Fsorry.'"
OL,14,FThis is how Steve Brisley, from
OL,15,FBridgend, recalls being reunited with
OL,16,Fhis brother-in-law after 16 months of
OL,17,Fnot knowing whether he was alive or
OL,18,Fdead.
