OL,3,C'Hope is all we had': Man reunited
OL,4,Cwith brother-in-law held hostage by
OL,5,CHamas
OL,7,FSteve's brother-in-law Eli Sharabi was
OL,8,Fkidnapped by Hamas from Kibbutz Be'eri
OL,9,Fin Israel as part of the attack on 7
OL,10,FOctober, 2023.
OL,12,FHis family have been campaigning for
OL,13,Fhis release for over a year.
OL,15,FSteve explained that he only found out
OL,16,Fthat Eli was alive the day before he
OL,17,Fwas freed, when Hamas announced which
OL,18,Fhostages would be released on 8
OL,19,FFebruary this year.
