OL,3,C'Hope is all we had': Man reunited
OL,4,Cwith brother-in-law held hostage by
OL,5,CHamas
OL,7,FSteve said: "It's been incredibly
OL,8,Fdifficult, but hope is all we had to
OL,9,Fhold on to."
OL,11,FHe continued: "We had to keep going
OL,12,Funtil the end, whatever that end was
OL,13,Fgoing to be. Whether he was going to
OL,14,Fbe coming home to be buried or
OL,15,Freunited with us. Thankfully it was to
OL,16,Fbe reunited with us."
