OL,3,C'Hope is all we had': Man reunited
OL,4,Cwith brother-in-law held hostage by
OL,5,CHamas
OL,7,FDuring the handover of hostages, Eli
OL,8,Fhad expressed how much he was looking
OL,9,Fforward to seeing his family again and
OL,10,Fbeing reunited with his wife and
OL,11,Fdaughters.
OL,13,FIt was only when he was being
OL,14,Ftransported from Gaza to Israel that
OL,15,Fhe asked, "Are Lianne and the girls
OL,16,Fwaiting for me?" to which an Israeli
OL,17,Fsolider broke the news that they had
OL,18,Fbeen murdered.
