OL,3,C'Hope is all we had': Man reunited
OL,4,Cwith brother-in-law held hostage by
OL,5,CHamas
OL,7,FWhilst Eli Sharabi was in captivity,
OL,8,Fhis wife Lianne and their teenage
OL,9,Fdaughters, Noiya and Yahel, were shot
OL,10,Fdead by Hamas while hiding in their
OL,11,Fsafe room.
OL,13,FOn 8 February this year, Hamas
OL,14,Freleased Eli Sharabi along with Ohad
OL,15,FBen Ami, 56, and Or Levy, 34, in
OL,16,Fexchange for 183 Palestinian prisoners
OL,17,Fas part of the ongoing ceasefire deal.
