OL,3,C'Hope is all we had': Man reunited
OL,4,Cwith brother-in-law held hostage by
OL,5,CHamas
OL,7,FSteve Brisley watched his brother-in-
OL,8,Flaw be freed on TV from his home in
OL,9,FBridgend, and said that he was unsure
OL,10,Fwhether it was really him due to his
OL,11,Fapperance.
OL,13,FSteve said, "The moment we had waited
OL,14,F16 months for, we were expecting it to
OL,15,Fbe rather more joyful than it was.
OL,17,F"The horror of seeing the state of him
OL,18,Fas he came out of the Hamas vehicle,
OL,19,Fhe was unrecognisable."
