OL,3,C'Hope is all we had': Man reunited
OL,4,Cwith brother-in-law held hostage by
OL,5,CHamas
OL,7,F"He looked so different, he was pale,
OL,8,Fgaunt, had clearly lost huge amount of
OL,9,Fweight."
OL,11,F"He didn't seem to be the Eli we knew
OL,12,Fand loved because the light, the
OL,13,Fspark, seemed to have gone in his
OL,14,Feyes."
OL,16,FIn a statement, Prime Minister Keir
OL,17,FStarmer said he was "dismayed" to see
OL,18,Fthe "frail condition" of Eli Sharabi
OL,19,Fand the circumstances of his release.
