OL,3,C'Hope is all we had': Man reunited
OL,4,Cwith brother-in-law held hostage by
OL,5,CHamas
OL,7,FHe said: "I shared the relief of so
OL,8,Fmany at Eli Sharabi's release earlier
OL,9,Ftoday but was dismayed to see his
OL,10,Ffrail condition and the circumstances
OL,11,Fof his release.
OL,13,F"Having met his relatives I appreciate
OL,14,Fthe deep pain they have endured and my
OL,15,Fthoughts are with them."
